By Thomas Godfray, [Printed at London : [1534?]]
Place of publication and printer's name from colophon; publication date conjectured by STC. Selections from the Bible. Signatures: A-G H⁴. Reproductions of the original in the Cambridge University Library. Appears at reel 49:9 and at reel 230:7 (same copy filmed twice).
